#. <section class="sutta" id="sn2.28"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn2.28:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 2"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 2"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn2.28:0.2"
msgid "3. Nānātitthiyavagga"
msgstr "3. Various Sectarians"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn2.28:0.3"
msgid "28. Nandivisālasutta"
msgstr "28. With Nandivisāla"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.28:1.1"
msgid ""
"Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho nandivisālo devaputto bhagavantaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi:"
msgstr ""
"Standing to one side, the god Nandivisāla addressed the Buddha in verse:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.28:2.1"
msgid "“Catucakkaṃ navadvāraṃ,"
msgstr "“Four are its wheels, and nine its doors;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.28:2.2"
msgid "puṇṇaṃ lobhena saṃyutaṃ;"
msgstr "it’s filled with greed and tied up;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.28:2.3"
msgid "Paṅkajātaṃ mahāvīra,"
msgstr "and it’s born from a bog. Great hero,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.28:2.4"
msgid "kathaṃ yātrā bhavissatī”ti."
msgstr "how am I supposed to live like this?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.28:3.1"
msgid "“Chetvā naddhiṃ varattañca,"
msgstr "“Having cut the strap and harness—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.28:3.2"
msgid "icchālobhañca pāpakaṃ;"
msgstr "wicked desire and greed—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.28:3.3"
msgid "Samūlaṃ taṇhamabbuyha,"
msgstr "and having plucked out craving, root and all:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.28:3.4"
msgid "evaṃ yātrā bhavissatī”ti."
msgstr "that’s how you’re supposed to live like this.”"
